            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>即溶咖啡被验出含「壮阳药」 HKTVmall ：「已即时下架货品」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/hktvmall/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hktvmall</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/hktvmall/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 09:29:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HKTVmall]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[昔多芬]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[东革阿里即溶咖啡]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272381</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">衞生署表示，一款名为「东革阿里即溶咖啡」的产品被检出含有受管制的处方药物「昔多芬」，并呼吁市民切勿购买或服用此产品。网购平台 HKTVmall 回复媒体查询时确认，该平台有一间商户曾售卖此产品，但已迅速下架。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272384 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-694x186.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="186" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-694x186.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲HKTVmall 已下架「东革阿里即溶咖啡」（图片来源：<a href="https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E6%9C%9B%E6%99%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/B0631001/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81/%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9/%E6%9D%B1%E9%9D%A9%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A18%E5%8C%85/p/B0631001_S_4897136810032">HKTVmall</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「东革阿里即溶咖啡」早前被发现产品含有「昔多芬」，HKTVmall 得悉货品在平台上放售，已立即下架，并会通知曾购买的顾客进行酌情处理及退款。HKTVmall 强调，平台内设有品质监察部门，订立严谨商户准则，并定期抽查商户商品，以确保产品合乎法规。一旦发现违规商品，会立即下架并对商户处以罚款或终止合作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272385 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mfile_1776925_1_2024-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mfile_1776925_1_2024-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mfile_1776925_1_2024.jpg 1208w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「东革阿里即溶咖啡」早前被发现产品含有壮阳药「昔多芬」（图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1776925-20241030.htm">RTHK</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「昔多芬」为一种常用于治疗勃起功能障碍的药物，其副作用包括头痛、低血压、头晕等，对心脏病患者尤其危险，如与治疗心绞痛的药物如「硝酸甘油」共同使用，可能导致血压骤降，造成严重的健康风险。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">有网民对事件作出讽刺反应，戏称「买咖啡送伟哥（壮阳药）」、「呼吁完销量好咗」，并在讨论区留言「即刻扫货」等。HKTVmall 表示会继续密切监察，并配合政府检查和规范。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1272388" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2-694x362.png" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2-694x362.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272387 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-602x580.png" alt="" width="602" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-602x580.png 602w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1.png 666w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 602px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民戏称「买咖啡送伟哥（壮阳药）」、「呼吁完销量好咗」及「即刻扫货」（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3813005/page/1">LIHKG</a>）</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1776925-20241030.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3813005/page/1">LIHKG</a>、<a href="https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E6%9C%9B%E6%99%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/B0631001/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5/%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81/%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9/%E6%9D%B1%E9%9D%A9%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A18%E5%8C%85/p/B0631001_S_4897136810032">HKTVmall</a>、<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20241031/s00001/1730348470085/hktvmall%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E5%90%AB%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1-%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E6%9B%BE%E5%94%AE">明报</a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2032762/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%8D%B3%E6%BA%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA-%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E8%B2%B7-HKTV-mall%E5%8D%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%88%B2%E8%AC%94%E6%9B%B2%E7%B7%9A%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3-%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8">星岛日报</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/hktvmall/software/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>桌球「火箭」奥苏利云优才计划成香港居民，喜爱香港税制好、美食多、自然环境佳</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/ronnie-antonio-osullivan/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ronnie-antonio-osullivan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/ronnie-antonio-osullivan/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 08:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运动科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[奥苏利云]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌球]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[火箭]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272396</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">英国桌球名将绰号奥苏利云透过「优秀人才入境计划」成为香港居民。入境处宣布消息，并发布奥苏利云抵港的影片，展示他经香港居民柜枱入境的过程。入境处处长郭俊峰亲自与奥苏利云会面，向他了解选择香港作为新居住地的原因。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272398 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-1-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-1-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241031at-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲奥苏利云透过「优秀人才入境计划」成为香港居民（图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1777000-20241031.htm">RTHK</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">奥苏利云表示，过去他多次来港参赛，曾于香港享受美好时光并结识不少朋友，并且对香港良好的税制及美食印象深刻。他曾在香港国际桌球明星挑战赛记者会上坦言喜爱香港的自然环境，特别热衷于在西贡跑山，感受到香港的活力。他还赞赏香港一切「都好正」，并期待在此地能够更放松地生活，同时希望未来能为香港社区作出贡献。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">现年 48 岁的奥苏利云，拥有传奇的桌球生涯，自 17 岁出道便登上巅峰，并以其出杆速度快而被冠以「火箭」之名。奥苏利云世锦赛成绩显赫，7 夺世界冠军，是桌球界之冠。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1777000-20241031.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=581265">Now</a>、<a href="https://www.singtaousa.com/2024-10-30/%E6%A1%8C%E7%90%83%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E5%A5%A7%E8%98%87%E5%88%A9%E9%9B%B2%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%81%E5%BE%AA%E3%80%8C%E5%84%AA%E7%A7%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%A8%88/5039771#page6">星岛日报</a>、<a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Flive%2Fsnooker%2F58002885%2Fpage%2F3&amp;psig=AOvVaw2Y_pCv1HmlOMO32htp2o9d&amp;ust=1730441973106000&amp;source=images&amp;cd=vfe&amp;opi=89978449&amp;ved=0CBcQjhxqFwoTCPi0huv8t4kDFQAAAAAdAAAAABAE">BBC</a>、<a href="https://www.instagram.com/hongkongimmigrationdept/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;ig_rid=4ebc335b-69e3-429b-95d7-4561aff62789">香港入境事务处</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/ronnie-antonio-osullivan/fun-tech/">桌球「火箭」奥苏利云优才计划成香港居民，喜爱香港税制好、美食多、自然环境佳</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
